# Directions to L100 Focused Attacks Trainer (Yujoki, mob 6785)

say { "Hello";
	say Hello %n, how can I assist you?;
	}

say { "trainer";
	tell %n Finding your next trainer is part of your training.;
	tell %n However, I can give you a hint....;
	tell %n Past the dried dusty landscape of the desert,;
	tell %n before the great Veldt lies a mountain.;
	tell %n Climb it's splintery rock face and there;
	tell %n shall you find your answer.;
	}
